{
  "stem": "107.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I learned on his side, he gave courses in graphology, that skill which became very helpful to me in later life.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The science of handwriting analysis.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not only for purpose of identification, but by purpose of reading character, personality traits.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's not a religion.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's not a matter of believing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, it is a very practical and very helpful thing for people who know-- I know there are many charlatans who just-- who make hocus pocus out of it, and are like psychics, which has nothing to do with it.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, I have a library of handouts of very serious books.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And have even given courses here.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And at the same time, I was employed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I had a little income there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that my father had a little income.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had  a little income.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we didn't have to live from social support.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My sister at that time, went to Holland, where we had family.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not close family, but somehow cousins of cousins or second-degree cousins who employed her as household help.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was the only way the Dutch government would allow people, immigrants, to work.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so she thought she could survive and basically did at that time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Needless to say, during that period, I wrote to everybody, to the universities, to find some way to get out.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the only thing I didn't do-- and some people saved their lives by doing this-- was to go in an illegal transport to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Some of these peoples were-- from-- these transports, died on the way.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But quite a number of people, younger people, made these journeys on Turkish miserable boats, and somehow got to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And some of my friends did it and their wives.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I probably-- it was a complex situation.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
